# Screenshots Directory

This directory contains UI screenshots for user documentation.

## Naming Convention

Use descriptive names that indicate the feature and state:
- `signin-page.png`
- `dashboard-overview.png`
- `create-portfolio-form.png`
- `add-investment-modal.png`
- `portfolio-chart-view.png`

## Screenshot Guidelines

- Resolution: 1920x1080 recommended
- Format: PNG for clarity
- Annotate when necessary to highlight features
- Update screenshots when UI changes significantly
